I.O.U.S.A.;;86;;88;;PG;;Will the United States of America go broke in your lifetime? This documentary examines the myriad reasons why such a dangerous outcome is a distinct possibility. In the opinion of some, as the baby boomer generation ages, entitlement programs will be strained to the breaking point, and an astronomical defense budget and excessive national debt threaten to hurl the country over the financial brink. If the U.S. is not prepared to change its ways, the film warns, we'd better be ready for disaster.;;Documentary;;Patrick Creadon;;2008;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_o_u_s_a